How to run o nthe Kubernetes --- 

1 - install Kubernetes ctl on youre device 
2 - Once done try running. 
3 - Create app (using name space i have used hr-suite)
4 - using command such as ---     kubectl create namespace hr-suite
5 - Please use Powershell and run them in seperate shell windows ---- 

 kubectl port-forward -n hr-suite svc/frontend-service 8080:80

 kubectl port-forward -n hr-suite svc/api-service 3001:3001

 kubectl port-forward -n hr-suite svc/payroll-api-service 4000:4000

 kubectl port-forward -n hr-suite svc/payroll-frontend-service 8081:80

-----------

kubectl get pods,svc -n hr-suite
kubectl rollout restart deploy -n hr-suite






